1374
01:18:47,350 --> 01:18:50,150
Akane, I think I actually might know him.

1375
01:18:50,180 --> 01:18:51,580
- Huh?

1376
01:18:51,620 --> 01:18:53,590
- We went to the same school together.

1377
01:18:53,620 --> 01:18:55,350
His name was Ron back then.

1378
01:18:56,520 --> 01:18:59,360
