1379
01:18:59,390 --> 01:19:02,130
(mellow music)

1380
01:19:09,030 --> 01:19:10,040
After graduation?

1381
01:19:11,200 --> 01:19:13,140
Well, you see, my biggest goal right now

1382
01:19:13,170 --> 01:19:14,510
