1383
01:19:15,470 --> 01:19:16,680
- If you're gonna be an alchemist,

1384
01:19:16,710 --> 01:19:18,310
then I'm gonna be better than you

1385
01:19:18,340 --> 01:19:20,650
as the greatest wizard in the whole world!

1386
01:19:21,880 --> 01:19:22,920
- [Pipo] Hm?

1387
01:19:22,950 --> 01:19:25,180
I heard a rumor that he became an apprentice

1388
01:19:25,220 --> 01:19:26,220
to Master Kamadoma.

1389
01:19:26,250 --> 01:19:29,190
So I wonder why he looks like that.

1390
01:19:29,220 --> 01:19:32,760
(light fast-paced music)

1391
01:19:32,790 --> 01:19:34,660
- There's a guard house up ahead.

1392
01:19:34,690 --> 01:19:36,630
We can catch up once they stop him.

1393
01:19:39,370 --> 01:19:40,300
Huh?

1394
01:19:40,330 --> 01:19:41,570
What the?

1395
01:19:42,330 --> 01:19:44,900
(mellow music)

1396
01:19:46,140 --> 01:19:48,910
- Cats know how to get a good nappin', don't they?

1397
01:19:48,940 --> 01:19:52,580
(light fast-paced music)

1398
01:20:07,130 --> 01:20:08,290
(tense music)

1399
01:20:08,330 --> 01:20:09,930
- If the armored mouse is here, then-

1400
01:20:09,960 --> 01:20:11,930
- [Pipo] Zan Gu must be here too.

1401
01:20:23,440 --> 01:20:25,010
- I managed to snatch some good stuff

1402
01:20:25,040 --> 01:20:26,850
from the market for us.

1403
01:20:36,360 --> 01:20:38,120
It's finally time.

1404
01:20:38,160 --> 01:20:39,460
- What are they gonna do?

1405
01:20:39,490 --> 01:20:41,260
- I'll read their lips.

1406
01:20:41,290 --> 01:20:42,060
Stay still.

1407
01:20:45,560 --> 01:20:47,070
- It'll go just as planned.

1408
01:20:47,100 --> 01:20:50,900
The armored mouse's new cannon is gonna destroy that well!

1409
01:20:50,940 --> 01:20:51,540
(cackles)

1410
01:20:51,570 --> 01:20:53,240
- It's gonna be a blast.

1411
01:20:53,270 --> 01:20:54,510
What do we do?

1412
01:20:54,540 --> 01:20:56,280
They're gonna destroy the timeless rain well.

1413
01:20:56,310 --> 01:20:57,380
- Is that bad?

1414
01:20:57,410 --> 01:20:59,380
- [Pipo] Yes, that will is essential

1415
01:20:59,410 --> 01:21:00,710
for this world's survival.

1416
01:21:04,150 --> 01:21:05,820
- Hey, aren't you gonna eat?

1417
01:21:05,850 --> 01:21:07,690
