1418
01:21:07,720 --> 01:21:09,890
but we can't change our minds now.

1419
01:21:10,890 --> 01:21:13,290
That well is the cause of all this trouble.

1420
01:21:13,330 --> 01:21:14,490
You said if it's gone,

1421
01:21:14,530 --> 01:21:17,330
