1422
01:21:17,360 --> 01:21:20,000
- One of the shining bugs died.

1423
01:21:20,030 --> 01:21:20,830
- Hm?

1424
01:21:21,870 --> 01:21:24,800
It's fine, we only need like one or two anyway.

1425
01:21:24,840 --> 01:21:26,070
(clangs)

1426
01:21:26,100 --> 01:21:27,270
