1441
01:22:08,480 --> 01:22:10,450
(men gasps)

1442
01:22:10,480 --> 01:22:12,150
The plating has now been removed.

1443
01:22:15,050 --> 01:22:16,660
(Chii grunts)

1444
01:22:16,690 --> 01:22:19,160
- Where did Akane run off to?

1445
01:22:19,190 --> 01:22:22,130
Well, I'm sure she'll come back if I wait here for her.

1446
01:22:25,000 --> 01:22:27,570
(sighs)

1447
01:22:27,600 --> 01:22:31,800
Man, what a great haul. (chuckles)

1448
01:22:31,840 --> 01:22:34,040
(sighs)

1449
01:22:34,070 --> 01:22:35,140
- It's impossible.

1450
01:22:35,170 --> 01:22:37,340
There's no way we can stop them on our own.

1451
01:22:37,380 --> 01:22:38,510
- They may have a cannon

1452
01:22:38,540 --> 01:22:40,510
